title: Ep - 79 - DAVID PARNES – MILLION DOLLAR LISTING LOS ANGELES
description:
David Parnes from Million Dollar Listing Los Angeles explains why the agents spend so much money on broker showings, why so many people are buying homes in Encino, if he ever runs into Chad Rogers, and gives an update on his wife’s pregnancy. His brother Michael joins in the conversation and gives up an update on his health after his brain tumor diagnosis. 


Bill Crane from Philadelphia reviews the John Stamos episode of Who Do You Think You Are on TLC.


Celebrity stylist Ali Levine discusses why she and her husband agreed to do the show Stripped on Bravo.
